rows.label: qst105702_msg0002
rows.name:
To think you'd chase me
all the way here...mo...

rows.label: qst105702_msg0021
rows.name:
Are you surprised to
see Zadazan here, mo?

rows.label: qst105702_msg0022
rows.name:
Fomomo... Did you come chasing
after Bahn-sama's money, mo?

rows.label: qst105702_msg0023
rows.name:
We, Lindwurm, are hidden
everywhere, watching you all, mo.

rows.label: qst105702_msg0051
rows.name:
...Yes. To Lindwurm, you all are
nothing but an obstacle, mo.

rows.label: qst105702_msg0052
rows.name:
Zadazan will crush you to
pieces right here, mo.

rows.label: qst105702_msg0008
rows.name:
Heheh, but before that... I'll
tell you something good, mo.

rows.label: qst105702_msg0071
rows.name:
Bahn-sama's money is for
Lindwurm's ideal...mo...

rows.label: qst105702_msg0072
rows.name:
...it was used for the destruction
of the Superbian Empire, mo!

rows.label: qst105702_msg0073
rows.name:
The more the Avaritia Trade Guild
prospers, the further the Empire
walks the path to ruin, mo.

rows.label: qst105702_msg0012
rows.name: Fomomomomo!! The talking is over, mo!

rows.label: qst105702_msg0013
rows.name:
I will test the power of this
thing, procured with Bahn-sama's
money, on you all, mo!
